'''Bere''' (''Hyena'' in English) imhuka yemusango ine makamba matema nebrown inokura kusvika pamhumhu wembwa. Iyi mhuka inowanikwa mu[[ziwumbe]] zve[[Africa]] neAsia. Bere imhuka inozivikanwa nokufamba usiku uye nemusana waro wakaita [[muteremuko]] unobva kumakumbo emberi uchidzika kuenda kumakumbo eshuru.

Bere rakasiyana nekatsi dzemusango pakuti rinobata dzimwe mhuka richishandisa mazino kwete makumbo ane nzwara sezvinoita [[mbada]].

